This is a project demonstrating next framework (a Java/GWT mobile framework for Smartphones and Tablets using HTML5 and MVC).

More information:
============
  http://nextinterfaces.com/
 

Demo:
============
  http://nextinterfaces.com/DEMO


Dependencies:
============
  Java5+
  GWT2.2+
  

Supported:
============
  iOS, iPhone, Android, BlackBerry O6+, PlayBook, HP webOS, Samsung bada

 
Installation
============
  Copy next.jar file(nextinterfaces/war/WEB-INF/next.jar) to your project and add it to your classpath.

  See the attached demo project for more information.